description: The nonzero difference between the Pascal {1,8,1} level triangle sequence and the {1,8,1} Catalan generalized triangle: t0(n,m)=Binomial[n, m]*Product[k!*(n + k)!/((m + k)!*(n - m + k)!), {k, 1, 7}]. A(n,k)=(3*n - 3*k + 1)A(n - 1, k - 1) + (3*k - 2)A(n - 1, k); t(n,m)=A(n,m)-t0(n,m). The first three levels and the external columns are zero and extracted.
